Project: Akademi Egitim Takip Sistemi
TechStack: Spring Boot (Java) backend, PostgreSQL, React frontend
Goal: Eğitim, Eğitmen, Sorumlu, Proje, Faaliyet, Paydaş, Ödeme yönetimi + login + loglama + raporlama.
Constraints:
 - Eğitim <-> Eğitmen: many-to-many
 - Eğitim <-> Sorumlu: many-to-many
 - Eğitim <-> Kategori: many-to-many
 - Eğitim -> Proje: optional, max 1
 - Faaliyet <-> Sorumlu: many-to-many
 - Paydaş <-> Sorumlu: many-to-many
 - Use migrations (Flyway or Liquibase)
 - Write unit & integration tests for backend (JUnit) and basic E2E for critical flows (Cypress)
Style:
 - Clean, well-documented code. Each file/class should have a short header comment explaining responsibility.
 - Provide SQL for table creation and index suggestions.
 - Provide API contract (OpenAPI/Swagger) for each endpoint.